INersa ithe ukwanda kwamacala enkohlakalo nokungaphathi ngendlela kwa-Eskom yikhona okwenze yanqaba ukuthi le nkampani ithole uR219 billion ebiwufuna. INersa yagunyaza ukuthi i-Eskom inganyusa amanani ngo-5.23% kuphela kanti itshele iNkankolo eNkulu ePitoli izolo, iNorth Gauteng, ukuthi lesi sinqumo yasithatha ukuvikela amakhasimende. U-Adv Rafik Bhana SC, weNersa wenze lezi zethulo ephendula isicelo se-Eskom. “I-Eskom ayiphethwe ngendlela ngakho ifuna amakhasimende athwale umthwalo. Le nkampani ihluleke ukulungisa izinto njengoba ibikhokha amabhonasi afinyelela ku-42% wenzuzo yayo okutshengisa ukungabinandaba nomphakathi.”